  "page": 209,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0002",
      "text": " 190",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0003",
      "text": "The EVFP protocol is used also when some N_Port or F_Port configuration information (see 8.3) are",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.93,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0004",
      "text": "changed by a management action. The EVFP messages may be carried in FC frames tagged with",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.96,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0005",
      "text": "the Port VF_ID if the EVFP protocol begins while the link is not performing VFT tagging (see 8.4.1).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        539.93,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0006",
      "text": "The EVFP messages are carried in FC frames tagged with the Control VF_ID if the EVFP protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        540.05,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0007",
      "text": "begins while the link is performing VFT tagging (see 8.4.2 and 8.4.3).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        105.64,
        400.97,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0008",
      "text": "8.4.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        118.22,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0009",
      "text": "Changing the VFT Tagging Mode",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        130.97,
        284.28,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0010",
      "text": "When a management action changes the Administrative Tagging Mode of a VF capable N_Port or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        540.05,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0011",
      "text": "F_Port that determined during initialization the peer supports the EVFP protocol, the FC_Port shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        540.03,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0012",
      "text": "determine if the link has to change its VFT Tagging mode (i.e., if it has to transition from tagging to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        539.97,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0013",
      "text": "untagging mode or from untagging to tagging mode) by acting as EVFP Initiator as follows. If the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        539.98,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0014",
      "text": "N_Port or F_Port is currently performing tagging, all EVFP protocol messages shall be tagged with",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.92,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0015",
      "text": "the Control VF_ID. If the N_Port or F_Port is currently not performing tagging, all EVFP protocol mes-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.05,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0016",
      "text": "sages shall be untagged.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        207.11,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0017",
      "text": "1) The EVFP Initiator shall start the EVFP transaction by sending the EVFP_SYNC message to",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        250.96,
        539.92,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0018",
      "text": "the EVFP Responder. The EVFP_SYNC message shall carry the updated Tagging Administra-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        262.96,
        540.03,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0019",
      "text": "tive Status (see 4.2.43.2.2), Port VF_ID, and the Locally-Enabled VF_ID List; and",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        274.96,
        481.28,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0020",
      "text": "2) The EVFP Responder shall reply with an LS_ACC carrying its Tagging Administrative Status,",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        298.96,
        540.06,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0021",
      "text": "Port VF_ID and Locally-Enabled VF_ID List. The EVFP Responder shall determine if VFT Tag-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        310.96,
        540.05,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0022",
      "text": "ging has to be changed on the link, according to table 126. The EVFP Responder:",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        322.96,
        484.67,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0023",
      "text": "A) if VFT Tagging has not to be changed, on completion of the Exchange terminates the EVFP",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        346.96,
        540.05,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0024",
      "text": "protocol; or",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        358.96,
        188.07,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0025",
      "text": "B) if VFT Tagging has to be changed, on completion of the Exchange shall perform a link ini-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        382.96,
        540.15,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0026",
      "text": "tialization.",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        394.96,
        182.37,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0027",
      "text": "On receiving the EVFP_SYNC LS_ACC, the EVFP Initiator shall determine if VFT Tagging has",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        418.96,
        539.99,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0028",
      "text": "to be changed on the link, according to table 126. The EVFP Initiator:",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        430.96,
        427.96,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0029",
      "text": "A) if VFT Tagging has not to be changed, on completion of the Exchange terminates the EVFP",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        454.96,
        540.05,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0030",
      "text": "protocol; or",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        466.96,
        188.07,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0031",
      "text": "B) if VFT Tagging has to be changed, shall participate in the link initialization initiated by the",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        490.96,
        539.96,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0032",
      "text": "EVFP Responder.",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        502.96,
        218.55,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0033",
      "text": "8.4.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        118.22,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0034",
      "text": "Adding or Removing Virtual Fabrics",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        526.96,
        298.77,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0035",
      "text": "When a management action changes the Locally-Enabled VF_ID List over a tagging N_Port or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.03,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0036",
      "text": "F_Port, the FC_Port shall initiate the EVFP protocol by acting as EVFP Initiator as follows. All EVFP",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.94,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0037",
      "text": "protocol messages shall be tagged with the Control VF_ID.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        356.5,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0038",
      "text": "1) The EVFP Initiator shall start the EVFP transaction by sending the EVFP_SYNC message to",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        598.96,
        539.91,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0039",
      "text": "the EVFP Responder. The EVFP_SYNC message shall carry the Tagging Administrative Sta-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        610.96,
        539.99,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0040",
      "text": "tus, Port VF_ID, and the updated Locally-Enabled VF_ID List (see 4.2.43.2.4);",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        622.96,
        467.4,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0041",
      "text": "2) The EVFP Responder shall reply with an LS_ACC carrying its Tagging Administrative Status,",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        647.02,
        540.06,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0042",
      "text": "Port VF_ID and Locally-Enabled VF_ID List. The EVFP Responder, depending on the resulting",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        659.02,
        539.99,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p209_s0043",
      "text": "operational VF_ID List (see 4.2.43.2.4):",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        671.02,
        296.78,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}